<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Macrocheilus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Macrocheilus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="91" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Macrocheilus</taxonomicName>
in the Oriental Region.
</paragraph>
